high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter with the toaster
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and go to the trash can
Slice the tomato in the trash can
Put the knife in the trash can
Grab a slice of the tomato from the trash can
Turn around and go to the oven
Put the tomato in the pan in the top left stove
Grab the pan from the top left stove
Turn around and go to the left of the table
Put the pan on the table

high_descs: Head towards the refrigerator then turn left, head towards the stove, then right towards the toaster.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the toaster.
Turn right then head towards the door then left towards the  trash can.
Take the knife the cut the tomato inside the trash can
Place the knife into the trash cash next to the tomato.
Pick up the tomato slice from inside the trash can.
Turn all the way then head towards the table, turn right then head towards the stove.
Place the tomato slice into the pan on the back left burner.
Pick up two pans from the stove, the pan on the left and right back burners.
Turn all the way around then head towards the door then right then head towards the table.
Place the two pans onto the table near the window.
anns.task_desc: Place two pans, one with a tomato slice inside, onto the table.
